data.title: Marriage Astrology
data.text:
We studied 30 years since your birth date from Jan. 02, 1903 to Dec. 31, 1932. The total number of analyzed dates are 10957. Out of so many dates, we have rejected 9314 dates (85.0%) as your marriage dates due to unfavourable transit and dashas.

Observations

In past, you had a very favorable time for marriage in 1914,1918,1913. In these year, planets influencing your marriage were forming favourable combinations.This means that either you got married in these years or you were very closer to getting married in case if you are not married.

We have performed a comprehensive assessment of your Kundali, which involves analyzing different aspects such as personality strength, relationship fullfillment derived from our AI/ML model, and along with planetary combinations that can either favor or disfavor love or arranged marriage. This analysis allows us to determine whether you are more suitable for a love or arranged marriage.

Personality Strength & Relationship Fulfillment

Your Kundali suggests a moderate personality and also a low likelihood of fulfilling your relationship desires.

You have a moderate personality, which means that it may take time for you to capture the attention and love of another person. You may also face challenges in marrying your desired partner. There is a high likelihood that you will end up marrying someone chosen by your parents or relatives.

Planetary Combinations

Your Kundali indicates that you possess the potential to successfully choose your life partner through the presence of one favorable combinations. These are -

Mo and Ve are in same house. There conjunct strength is 64.8%.
